"story_beats": {
      "hook": "The machine display is lit and the pump runs while the white cup under the spout remains completely dry.",
      "rising_tension": "Hands prove the obvious checks: water tank filled to the line, portafilter locked, cup centered, brew button pressed again, still no water.",
      "climax": "The tank is removed and turned toward the lens; a small red shipping plug is visible inside the inlet and pulled out with a pop.",
      "resolution": "The same button is pressed again and espresso drips into the same cup, changing the opening from a broken-product scene into a setup-mistake scene."
    }
